PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT DISTINCT CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME FROM CONTENTTYPES, RXSLOTCONTENT WHERE CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID = RXSLOTCONTENT.CONTENTTYPEID AND RXSLOTCONTENT.SLOTID = :"PSXParam/inlineslotid" AND (CONTENTTYPES.HIDEFROMMENU = 0 or CONTENTTYPES.HIDEFROMMENU is null) ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME
